{"lemma":"قَصْبَة","slug":"قَصْبَة","root":"ق.ص.ب","root_slug":"ق-ص-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ص-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35718","n35722"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut up (a slaughtered animal)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to curl, carve"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of قَصَبَ (qaṣaba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stalk","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reed, cane (especially sugarcane)","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thread, filament","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"وفلسقيتان أُخريان من بِلّوْر مربّط ففضة، مذهّبة الناحية الواحدة، مشبكة بجواهر، وفي وسطها درات، وفي الناحية الأخُرَى أَربع قصبات فضة مطلية بذهب، وكرنيب وكوز فضة مطليّان بذهب مجرى فيهما الجوهر.","english":"And two other flasks are of crystals twined with silver, gildened in one corner, netted with jewels, and in their mids pearls, and in the other corner four threads of silver thatched with gold, and a bowl and a mug of silver layered both with gold and woven with gemstones."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pipe","tags":["collective"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Back-formation from قَصَّاب (qaṣṣāb, “butcher”) borrowed from Aramaic קצבא / ܩܰܨܳܒܳܐ (qaṣṣābā), therewith forming a root ق ص ب (q ṣ b). Doublet of indigenous Arabic قَضَبَ (qaḍaba, “to cut off, to trim”).\n\nFrom the root ق ص ب (q ṣ b) of the aforementioned verb meaning “to be segment”, “to be cut into sections”, “to be severed”; stemming from a reed's divisions or from being collected as cut pieces; compare قَضْب (qaḍb)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35718","headword_ar":"قَصَبَهُ","root":"qSb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSobN","text_ar":"قَصْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * M, O, * K,) namely, a thing; (M;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqtSbhu","text_ar":"اقتصبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaba","text_ar":"قَصَبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aApa","text_ar":"الشَّاةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O, Msb, K,) aor. as above, (M, Msb,) and so the inf. n., (S, M, O, Msb,) said of the butcher, (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut up the sheep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat, into joints,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separate limbs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he separated the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bones called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSab","text_ar":"قَصَب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sheep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN lamo yuqoSabN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لَمْ يُقْصَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has not been circumcised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaSobu","text_ar":"القَصْبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ the act of cutting. ” (A.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabahu","text_ar":"قَصَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSobF","text_ar":"قَصْبً"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qS~bhu","text_ar":"قصّبهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoSibN","text_ar":"تَقْصِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attributed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"imputed, to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accused him of, a vice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, O, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reviled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vilified, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, K;) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut him with censure."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabahu","text_ar":"قَصَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, O, K,) namely, a camel, and [any] other [animal], (S, O,) or a man, (M, K,) and a beast, (M,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stopped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut short,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prevented,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his drinking, before he had satisfied his thirst."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaba","text_ar":"قَصَبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$urobahu","text_ar":"شُرْبَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abstained from his drinking before he had satisfied his thirst:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, O:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaba","text_ar":"قَصَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone], said of a camel, (As, M, K, TA,) aor. as above, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSobN","text_ar":"قَصْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quSuwbN","text_ar":"قُصُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he refused to drink:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he abstained from drinking the water, raising his head from it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before he had satisfied his thirst:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quSuwbN","text_ar":"قُصُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"satisfying of thirst by coming to the water &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaba AlmaA='a","text_ar":"قَصَبَ المَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSobN","text_ar":"قَصْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sucked up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sucked in, the water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.)       -A3-  It seems to be applied in the S that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaba","text_ar":"قَصَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. as above, also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He played upon a musical reed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pipe."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MF.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","S","O","Msb","A","ISk","As","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n35722","headword_ar":"قَصَبَةٌ","root":"qSb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph, in nine places. ―         -b2-  [It also, app., signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caneroll of a loom:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niyrN","text_ar":"نِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  And, app., (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mouth, which has the form of a short cylinder, in the middle of the upper part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the kind of leathern water-bag called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdap","text_ar":"مَزَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurotapN","text_ar":"خُرْتَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bone"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the nose;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabapu AlA^anofi","text_ar":"قَصَبَةُ الاَنْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the nasal bone."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A.) ―         -b5-  [And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shaft"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a well.] You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biy^orN musotaqiymapu AlqaSabapi","text_ar":"بِيْرٌ مُسْتَقِيمَةُ القَصَبَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A well of which the shaft is straight"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b6-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A well recently dug."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA.) ―         -b7-  And (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a country or town; (A;) and of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSor","text_ar":"قَصْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. pavilion, or palace]; (M, A, K;) and of a fortress; (A:) or of a fortress containing a building or buildings; or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle"},{"kind":"text","text":"of such a fortress, (TA,) and of a town or village: (S, L, Msb, TA: [Golius, reading"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiroyap","text_ar":"قِرْيَة"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaroyap","text_ar":"قَرْيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", assigns to it also the signification of the “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a water-skin: ”]) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSor","text_ar":"قَصْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pavilion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] itself; (M, K;) and ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fortress"},{"kind":"text","text":"itself, or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fortified castle such as is occupied by a commander and his forces:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xwj","text_ar":"خوج"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a town"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"village"},{"kind":"text","text":"[itself]: (M, K:) and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariym","text_ar":"حَرِيم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a house. (T and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hrm","text_ar":"حرم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A city:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"city"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb) of the Sawád, (S,) or, [by a general application,] of a country: (M, Msb:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main, part"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) of a city (M) or of cities. (K: but in the TA this last meaning is given as the explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amoSaAri","text_ar":"الاَمْصَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabu","text_ar":"قَصَبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b8-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSiybapN","text_ar":"قَصِيبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places: ―         -b9-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiSaAbN","text_ar":"قِصَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["A","TA","M","K","S","Msb"]}]}}